title: 200,000 Tests Step Up The Fight Against Drug Drivers (Premier of Victoria)
text: ( Source : Premier of Victoria ) Two hundred thousand drivers will be checked for drugs over the next two years under a major expansion of Victoria 's roadside testing program. Money for 100 , 000 extra drug tests to nab drugged drivers starts
